title: Rusk Thick Body and Texture Amplifier, 6 Ounce
description: Gives fine, limp or lazy hair incredible body, volume and texture. Contains thermaplex, a unique ingredient, which activates with the heat of a blow-dryer to boost body and volume from the inside out.

title: Oscar by Oscar De La Renta for Women - 3.3 Ounce EDT Spray
description: Oscar by Oscar De La Renta for Women - 3.3 oz EDT SprayWhen applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied
